### Get all appointments for today
GET http://localhost:5000/api/appointments/today
Accept: application/json

###

### Book an appointment
POST http://localhost:5000/api/appointments/book
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "2023-12-15T14:00:00",
  "customerName": "Jane Doe"
}

###

### Update an appointment
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/appointments/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "2023-12-15T15:00:00",
  "customerName": "Jane Doe Updated"
}

###

### Delete an appointment
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/appointments/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Get system configuration
GET http://localhost:5000/api/configuration
Accept: application/json

###

### Update system configuration
POST http://localhost:5000/api/configuration/update
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "maxAppointmentsPerDay": 20,
  "holidays": [
    "2023-12-25"
  ]
}

###
